# KingdomWar — Full RPC Reference & curl Commands

Base URL: `http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/rpc/<rpc_name>`
Har request: `-H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '\"<escaped-json>\"'`

PowerShell mein backtick (`` ` ``) line-continuation, aur payload double-escaped (`\\\"`) hota hai jaisa neeche hai.

---

## Authentication

```powershell
$response = curl.exe -s "http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/account/authenticate/device?create=true" -u "defaultkey:" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "@body.json" | ConvertFrom-Json
$token = $response.token
```
(`body.json` mein `{"id": "<deviceId>"}` hona chahiye)

