## Army System (Volume 5 — NEW)

### `train_troops` — troops train karo, **buildingSlot zaroori hai** (per-Barracks queue)
```powershell
curl.exe -s -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/rpc/train_troops" `
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json" `
  -d '\"{\\\"unitId\\\":\\\"knight\\\",\\\"quantity\\\":10,\\\"buildingSlot\\\":\\\"10_10\\\"}\"'
```
Errors: `summon_hut_required`, `no_such_barracks_at_slot`, `queue_full`, `unknown_unit`, `army_cap_exceeded`, `insufficient_resources`
Note: units **trickle in one at a time** as each one's `train_time_seconds` elapses — not all at once at the end.

### `heal_troops` — wounded troops heal karo, **buildingSlot zaroori hai** (per-Hospital queue)
```powershell
curl.exe -s -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/rpc/heal_troops" `
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json" `
  -d '\"{\\\"unitId\\\":\\\"knight\\\",\\\"quantity\\\":5,\\\"buildingSlot\\\":\\\"12_12\\\"}\"'
```
Errors: `summon_hut_required`, `no_such_hospital_at_slot`, `heal_queue_full`, `insufficient_wounded`, `unknown_unit`, `insufficient_resources`
Note: same trickle behavior as training — units return to `army` one at a time.

### `send_reinforcement` — troops kisi Temple/Fortress/Citadel ko bhejo
```powershell
curl.exe -s -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/rpc/send_reinforcement" `
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json" `
  -d '\"{\\\"x\\\":5,\\\"y\\\":5,\\\"troops\\\":{\\\"knight\\\":3}}\"'
```
Errors: `not_reinforceable_target` (agar tile temple/fortress/citadel nahi hai), `insufficient_troops:<unitId>`, `structure_garrison_full`

### `recall_reinforcement` — bheji hui reinforcement wapis bulao
```powershell
curl.exe -s -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:7350/v2/rpc/recall_reinforcement" `
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json" `
  -d '\"{\\\"x\\\":5,\\\"y\\\":5}\"'
```
Errors: `no_garrison_here`

